  <main class="container content">
    <h1>Our Aim</h1>
    <p class="lead">Educive Foundation aims to make AI education accessible to students from underprivileged backgrounds by:</p>

    <ul class="goals">
      <li><strong>Foundational Training:</strong> Workshops on Python, data literacy and ML basics.</li>
      <li><strong>Mentorship:</strong> One-to-one mentorship and group projects with volunteers.</li>
      <li><strong>Research Pathways:</strong> Bridge students to internships, research labs and open projects.</li>
      <li><strong>Resources:</strong> Free learning materials, recorded sessions and curated reading lists.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Short-term targets (6–12 months)</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Run 8 beginner workshops (online and in-person)</li>
      <li>Mentor 30 students on capstone projects</li>
      <li>Establish partnerships with 3 research labs for internship slots</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Long-term vision</h2>
    <p>To create a self-sustaining community where motivated students from any background can learn AI, contribute to research, and access careers in technology.</p>
  </main>

