    <p class="lead">Help us understand needs and design better programs. Choose one of the options below:</p>

    <h2>Option A — Embed Google Form (recommended)</h2>
    <p>Create a Google Form (https://forms.google.com) with your questions, then in the form: Send &gt; &lt;&gt; (embed) &gt; copy iframe code and paste below (replace the src with your form's embed URL).</p>

    <!-- Replace YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_EMBED_URL below with the embed URL from Google Forms -->
